animeTitle: God Eater Reso Nantoka Gekijou: Nagerareta Shokupan
animeDescription: Short anime inspired by the iOS and Android mobile game God Eater Resonant Ops.Introduces the characters through their first day of school. Resonant Ops continues the story of God Eater 2 Rage Burst, which in turn is a sequel to God Eater Burst, and is set 4 years after the latter's story, moving the setting "at long last" toward the Fenrir Headquarters in the year 2078.
